short.ar: مع ريكس ، يجب عليك التغلب على العقبات على المسار وتسجيل أعلى مستوى ممكن.
short.am: ከሬክስ ጋር, በሐዲዱ ላይ ያሉ እንቅፋቶችን ተቋቁሞ የቻልከውን ያህል ከፍተኛ ውጤት ማግኘት አለብዎት.
short.bg: С Rex трябва да преодолеете препятствията на пистата и да отбележите колкото можете по-високо.
short.bn: রেক্সের সাথে, আপনাকে অবশ্যই ট্র্যাকের বাধাগুলি অতিক্রম করতে হবে এবং আপনি যতটা সম্ভব উচ্চ স্কোর করতে পারেন।

short.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,lt,pt_BR,pt_: With Rex, you must overcome the obstacles on the track and score as high as you can.
short.es: Con Rex, debes superar los obstáculos en la pista y puntuar lo más alto que puedas.

short.gu: રેક્સ સાથે, તમારે ટ્રેક પરના અવરોધોને દૂર કરવા જોઈએ અને તમે કરી શકો તેટલું ઊંચું સ્કોર કરવું જોઈએ.
short.he: עם רקס, אתה חייב להתגבר על המכשולים על המסלול ולקבל ציון גבוה ככל שאתה יכול.
short.hi: रेक्स के साथ, आप ट्रैक पर बाधाओं को दूर करने और आप कर सकते हैं के रूप में उच्च के रूप में स्कोर करना चाहिए।
short.hr: S Rexom morate prevladati prepreke na stazi i postići što je više moguće.
short.hu: A Rex segítségével le kell győznöd az akadályokat a pályán, és olyan magas pontszámot kell elérned, amennyire csak tudsz.

short.it: Con Rex, devi superare gli ostacoli in pista e segnare il più alto possibile.

short.kn: ರೆಕ್ಸ್ ನೊಂದಿಗೆ, ನೀವು ಟ್ರ್ಯಾಕ್ ನಲ್ಲಿರುವ ಅಡೆತಡೆಗಳನ್ನು ನಿವಾರಿಸಬೇಕು ಮತ್ತು ನಿಮಗೆ ಸಾಧ್ಯವಾದಷ್ಟು ಹೆಚ್ಚು ಸ್ಕೋರ್ ಮಾಡಬೇಕು.
short.ko: Rex를 사용하면 트랙의 장애물을 극복하고 가능한 한 높은 점수를 얻어야합니다.
short.lv: Izmantojot Rex, jums ir jāpārvar šķēršļi trasē un jāsasniedz tik augsts rezultāts, cik vien iespējams.
short.ml: റെക്സ് ഉപയോഗിച്ച്, നിങ്ങൾ ട്രാക്കിലെ തടസ്സങ്ങൾ തരണം ചെയ്യുകയും നിങ്ങൾക്ക് കഴിയുന്നത്ര ഉയർന്ന സ്കോർ നേടുകയും വേണം.
short.mr: रेक्ससह, आपण ट्रॅकवरील अडथळ्यांवर मात केली पाहिजे आणि शक्य तितके उच्च गुण मिळवले पाहिजेत.

short.nl: Met Rex moet je de obstakels op de baan overwinnen en zo hoog mogelijk scoren.

short.sw: Ukiwa na Rex, lazima ushinde vikwazo kwenye wimbo na ufunge juu kadri uwezavyo.
short.ta: ரெக்ஸ் உடன், நீங்கள் பாதையில் உள்ள தடைகளை கடக்க வேண்டும் மற்றும் உங்களால் முடிந்தவரை அதிக மதிப்பெண் பெற வேண்டும்.
short.te: రెక్స్ తో, మీరు ట్రాక్ పై అడ్డంకులను అధిగమించాలి మరియు మీకు సాధ్యమైనంత ఎక్కువ స్కోరు చేయాలి.
short.th: ด้วยเร็กซ์คุณต้องเอาชนะอุปสรรคในสนามแข่งและทําคะแนนให้สูงที่สุดเท่าที่จะทําได้
short.tr: Rex ile pistteki engelleri aşmalı ve olabildiğince yüksek puan almalısınız.
short.uk: З Рексом ви повинні подолати перешкоди на трасі і набрати якомога вище.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you ready for dinosaur game fun with 2 different modes! Make the highest score and show your talent. Two Rex is a fun dinosaur jumping simulator that can be played in single and two-player modes. The game aims to get the highest scores by jumping over the obstacles with your cute dinosaur character. Although it may seem simple at first, as the game progresses, the obstacles will accelerate, and the difficulty level will increase. It would help if you aimed for the highest scores using quick reflexes.

The most outstanding feature of the game is that it can be played in single-player and two-player modes. If you like to play alone, the single-player mode appeals to you, while if you want to have a pleasant time with your friend or family, you can choose the two-player mode. Two Rex game will be waiting for you whether playing alone or competing with a friend.

Your reflexes and speed are important as your goal in the game is to achieve the highest score. You can earn points by jumping over obstacles. As each level progresses, more obstacles will be encountered, and with it, the game's difficulty level will increase. This will draw you more into the game.

Two Rex will take you to the dinosaur world with colorful and fun graphics. Players of all ages can easily play it thanks to simple controls. Enjoy jumping with dinosaurs with Two Rex, Whether alone or competing with a friend.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Two Rex 2 Player Game Features
✓ Little Graphics
✓ Infinity Level
✓ Basic control
✓ 2 Different Mode

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Two Rex 2 Player Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
